verbose_text: Real-time PCR data showed that when IFN-JAK-STAT pathway was blocked by Ruxolitinib, transfection with poly (dA :d T) still induced expressions of ISGs, including IFIT1-3, ISG15 and Mx1, though the expression levels were lower than that in MSCs without Ruxolitinib treatment (XREF_FIG).
evidence: IFN-JAK-STAT pathway was blocked by Ruxolitinib
